# Per-run artifacts. Smoke evidence already tracked stays; new local runs are ignored.
# (Git ignores untracked paths only; already-tracked smoke runs are unaffected.)
runs/**/*
!runs/commit-msg/
!runs/commit-msg/**
!runs/deeper/
!runs/deeper/smoke-chain/
!runs/deeper/smoke-chain/**
!runs/deeper/smoke-branch/
!runs/deeper/smoke-branch/**
!runs/deeper/harness-smoke/
!runs/deeper/harness-smoke/**

# Harness scratch
**/.prompt-*.txt

# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo

# Editor / OS
.DS_Store
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
